------------------------------------------------------------------------

##  Database Used

All queries in this repository are based on the **ClassicModels MySQL
sample database**.

Download here:\
https://www.mysqltutorial.org/mysql-sample-database.aspx

------------------------------------------------------------------------

##  How to Import in MySQL Workbench

1.  Open MySQL Workbench\
2.  Go to **Server \> Data Import**\
3.  Select the downloaded `classicmodels.sql` file\
4.  Click **Start Import**\
5.  Refresh schemas

